{"tid":1935161,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺蔓延人潮稀少　子瑜帶頭「大街亂舞」TWICE笑歪","createTime":"2020-03-20T11:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T14:08:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e623d42eb95b97cd9a11c6b1a810591b9233300f","tid":1935161,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T11:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1584696417-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a-696x418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F1584696417-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a-696x418.jpg&h=15aebf9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情在韓擴散，熱門商圈不見以往人潮與觀光客，近期因為疫情取消所有活動的TWICE，趁著放假到平時不易出入的公共場所，今（20日）就在IG上傳成員玩VR遊戲、大街上零偽裝跳舞的影片，笑翻粉絲留言「女神們喝醉了」，督促她們顧一下形象。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE在IG放上三段影片，寫下：「成員說影片很有趣要求上傳，所以上傳了！」第一則是她們體驗VR射擊遊戲，除了子瑜，其他人都被虛擬實境嚇到狂尖叫，拍攝者趁機嚇對方，場面逗趣。第二、三則是成員們零偽裝在大街上的片段，子瑜打頭陣搞怪走秀，MOMO跟志效站後方獨自熱舞，各個跳到欲罷不能，成員就喊：「精神&hellip;.」、「妳在幹嘛啦！」十分爆笑。<br />\n<br />\n三段影片雖然搞笑，但粉絲仍留言叮嚀偶像「記得戴口罩啦」、也說成員像是喝醉，「完了這是喝了幾瓶？」、「不是喝了酒，就是嗑藥了」，要大家顧及女神形象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/1584696428-921e845c9eecadb33934fe1f9a47776f-1392x835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F1584696428-921e845c9eecadb33934fe1f9a47776f-1392x835.jpg&h=29228c78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"434af05c448026474e7298b5d01491c0561a7204","tid":1935161,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T11:16:50.000Z","msg":"瑜仔咪中please<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b54198f29da800dd8a310d6af3826394f307ca","tid":1935161,"uid":138740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"無口罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91bc9d605a6bb8c308e27c5530d0296956b6aca","tid":1935161,"uid":14494,"like":1,"disl